info.sourceTextContent: ¿Ha venido? Presumo que no, porque mandé recado a su casa y no está allí ni sabe nadie su paradero. Te juro que me causa una pena... ¡pobrecilla! Si después de todo no tiene mal fondo. Entre estas desgraciadas, las hay con excelente natural y hasta con asomos de dignidad.
info.suspiciousTextContent: Where has he been? I sent word to his house and there was no one there and no one knows his whereabouts. I assumed he has been gone. That's a shame. After all, he had a pretty good background. Besides this unfortunate event, he posesses excellent natural skills and even shows signs of dignit
